			<p><st1:place w:st="on">
			Mission</st1:place> Objective:  Determine 
			if a small satellite platform and GaN-based Ultraviolet 
			photodetector sensor can be designed, built and operated by a team 
			of university students<o:p></o:p></p>
			<p>
			<i>Comment:  In 
